DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages ntp
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include ntp              # Install and run ntp with standard configurations.
include ntp::disable     # Disable ntp service.
include ntp::disableboot # Disable ntp service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include ntp::absent      # Remove ntp package.

DEPENDENCIES:
